Class ExtensionBasedPatternAnnotationValidator

    IPatternAnnotationValidator

    public class ExtensionBasedPatternAnnotationValidator
extends java.lang.Object
implements IPatternAnnotationValidator
    A type-safe wrapper created from a pattern annotation extension point together with validation-related methods. Such validators are instantiated in PatternAnnotationProvider.

    Zoltan Ujhelyi
